description:
This is a 36 minute workout called 'HIIT - 35 Minute Cycle Training Workout - Hill Training' from the channel Global Cycling Network.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Subscribe to GCN Training: https://gcn.eu/GCNTraining

This indoor cycle training video is a 35 minute HIIT (high intensity interval session) which is designed to help you improve your fitness.

Subscribe to GCN: http://gcn.eu/SubscribeToGCN
Get exclusive GCN gear in the GCN store! http://gcn.eu/BuyGCNKit_
Sign up to the GCN newsletter: http://gcn.eu/gcnnewsletter

Get fit with GCN! Increase your fitness and your climbing ability with this short indoor training session for turbo trainer or static bike. Designed to replicate a good session climbing big hills, this session is a great workout for the legs, core and of course to improve cardiovascular fitness. If you're not sweating buckets at the end, you're not doing it right!
